{"tid":1639414,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[鬼國認證］要用hk live map個app就要快手DL","createTime":"2019-10-08T15:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T00:32:40.000Z","uid":158766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8fabe19d881f9aeb5b980f0b0fbaf7c6ad51430e","tid":1639414,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"愚民日報班仆街啱啱寫左文屌APPLE唔下架hk live map，雖然個人覺得web版好過app，但想DL嘅巴絲就要快手。<br />\n<br />\n人民日報發文稱，有這麼一款地，名為提供交通資訊、方便市民出行，實則通報警方行蹤、便利違法活動。就是這麼一款地圖，在蘋果APP商店裏堂而皇之上架，讓香港的暴徒大搖大擺出來行兇，又大搖大擺逃避追捕。地圖的開發者毫不避諱，要為暴徒&ldquo;導航&rdquo;，用心險惡；蘋果公司的批准不加掩飾，要為暴徒&ldquo;護航&rdquo;，居心何在？外國的一些公司大概不明白中國人的情感和思維方式。歷史上飽受過欺凌的中國人從來沒有像今天這樣團結，在涉及大是大非問題上眼睛裏容不得沙子。讓&ldquo;毒軟件&rdquo;大行其道，便是對中國人情感的背叛；對香港事務的各種歪曲，都違背中國人民的民意。<br />\n<br />\n未搵source 睇住先 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfAEDsm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfAEDsm.png&h=0cf337bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d43186667c9775367552ba252c28c97756c2cb8","tid":1639414,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"94c115f297bad4c6b5a0ccfa134c4865a4898abf","tid":1639414,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:02.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"930cbbd348d437ee09e2380be7a0f977e8745d95","tid":1639414,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:12.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2d80a9a5ac143f7d35b4e4deb834bc6b2ab01d3f","tid":1639414,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOvk7m5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOvk7m5.png&h=8dc1241f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e71058bff5062d949b2b20ba1c056c56461db822","tid":1639414,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"aceac876df4cc509a1b94b00c8a5